@startuml project_overview
title Project Overview - SpeechNotes
"Usuario" as User
package "CLI / UI" {
  [cli/realtime.py] as CLI
  [cli/file.py]
}
package "Audio I/O" {
  [src/audio/capture.py] as Capture
}
package "Core / Client" {
  [src/core/riva_client.py] as RivaClient
  [python-clients/riva/client/asr.py]
}
package "Transcription Service" {
  [src/transcription/service.py] as TransService
  [src/transcription/formatters.py]
}
package "Storage / Notes" {
  [notas/*]
  [data/*]
}
package "GUI" {
  [src/gui/vad_gui.py]
}
package "Legacy / Scripts" {
  [legacy/transcribe_realtime.py]
  [scripts/*]
}

User --> CLI : inicia transcripción
CLI --> Capture : solicita audio
Capture --> RivaClient : envía chunks
RivaClient --> TransService : retorna texto parcial
TransService --> [notas/*] : guarda/format
CLI --> [notas/*] : solicita lectura/guardado

note right of RivaClient
  - Implementa cliente Riva
  - auth, streaming
end note

note left of TransService
  - Formatea salida (markdown, puntuación)
end note

@enduml
